adm4_pcode ? Administrative code for the barangay (ADM4 level).
date ? Reference date of the measurement.
freq ? Frequency of data collection (e.g., Y = yearly).
rwi_max ? Maximum relative wealth index value within the barangay.
rwi_mean ? Mean (average) relative wealth index value.
rwi_median ? Median relative wealth index value.
rwi_min ? Minimum relative wealth index value.
rwi_std ? Standard deviation (variation) of the relative wealth index values.
